  y'know!&quot; Bruni admonished. Borq quieted, but it was plain by the grin on
  his face that he was enjoying himself enormously. <BR><BR>As they ventured further into the cave, they could feel the heat emanating
  from the pools, and could hear a vast roaring somewhere ahead, as if from a
