  brunt of the damage and falling to the ground. Bruni walked over to what was
  left of Ahrvid. &quot;Hey Scaleybutt - see if ye can find his arms, will
  ye?&quot; Once the corpse was reassembled, Bruni resurrected and healed the
  shadowknight. &quot;There ye are - good as new. Good job, by the way.&quot;
