  suffering resurrection effects.... &quot;Right then, through that tunnel and
  we're almost there,&quot; he said, pointing north. &quot;At the end of the
  tunnel is the door that leads into Brell's halls.&quot; <BR><BR>Meanwhile, back at the Harpy's Head Tavern, a storm bellowed with rage as a
  cold darkness stretched its hand to the tavern as hate began to move closer.
  The faint echo of evil laughter and clattering bones....coming
  closer...closer...but there was another sound that demanded attention...the
