  ta drink it wid!&quot; A booming voice could be heard, &quot;Bruni, is that
  you? And did you say ALE!?&quot; <BR><BR>The voices faded away as the party sat down to wait. After a few minutes,
  Sara stood up and faced the door. &quot;Here goes,&quot; she said, and taking
  a deep breath, headed inside. &quot;Close your mouth boys,&quot; scolded
